                    <p>(According to present results.)</p>
                    <p>The above figures refer only to gold obtained in smelting houses, but not
                        from private refineries (especially from smelting old silver coin).</p>
                    <p>Of the gold obtained from German smelting houses, there was produced from
                        imported foreign ores: <table cols="2" rows="4">
                            <row>
                                <cell/>
                                <cell>Kilos.</cell>
